channel.description:
How would I go about centering the PVP and safe icon that are both right above the 108 - 126?

[img]http://puu.sh/9J0Mv/f92c6ba314.png[/img]


EDIT:

Fixed :)

[img]http://puu.sh/9J1Ug/af519422ab.png[/img]

RSInterface -> PVPInterface, PVPInterface2, PVPInterface3 -> the first setbounds() -> setBounds(21301, [b]430[/b], 285, 0, RSinterface);

Method for setBounds();
[code]public static void setBounds(int ID, int X, int Y, int frame, RSInterface RSinterface) {
		RSinterface.children[frame] = ID;
		RSinterface.childX[frame] = X;
		RSinterface.childY[frame] = Y;
	}[/code]

430 = X coordinate that is centered over the 123 - 128

Hope this helps anyone else who has the issue.
